dct_title_s: Map of property formerly belonging in the 12th Ward of the City of New York belonging to the estate of James A. Stewart, deceased
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Also shows names of modern landowners and locations of old buildings. Oriented with north to the upper left. Includes text.
dct_subject_sm: Stewart, J. A. (James A.)—Homes and haunts—Maps
dcat_theme_sm: Stewart, J. A. (James A.)—Homes and haunts—Maps
